### Quality Scoring API Examples
### Use with REST Client extensions like VS Code REST Client

# Set base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Complete Quality Evaluation with Auto-Regeneration
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/evaluate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "AI is revolutionizing how we work and live. Machine learning algorithms are becoming increasingly sophisticated, enabling computers to perform tasks that once required human intelligence. From healthcare to finance, AI applications are transforming industries and creating new opportunities for innovation.",
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "technology professionals",
    "purpose": "inform about AI trends",
    "keywords": ["AI", "machine learning", "healthcare", "finance"],
    "tone": "professional"
  },
  "thresholds": {
    "minimum": 7,
    "excellent": 8.5
  }
}

### 2. Simple Quality Scoring (No Regeneration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "The rapid advancement of artificial intelligence has transformed numerous industries. Companies are investing heavily in AI research and development to gain competitive advantages. This technological revolution is reshaping how businesses operate and deliver value to customers.",
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "business executives",
    "purpose": "explain AI business impact",
    "keywords": ["AI", "business", "investment", "competitive"],
    "tone": "professional"
  }
}

### 3. Individual Metric Scoring - Clarity
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/clarity
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "The implementation of artificial intelligence systems requires careful consideration of various factors including data quality, algorithm selection, and ethical implications. Organizations must establish robust governance frameworks to ensure responsible AI deployment.",
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "technical managers",
    "tone": "formal"
  }
}

### 4. Individual Metric Scoring - Relevance
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/relevance
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Digital marketing strategies have evolved significantly with the advent of social media platforms and data analytics. Modern marketers must leverage multiple channels and personalization techniques to reach target audiences effectively.",
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "marketing professionals",
    "purpose": "explain digital marketing evolution",
    "keywords": ["digital marketing", "social media", "analytics", "personalization"],
    "tone": "professional"
  }
}

### 5. Individual Metric Scoring - Depth
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/depth
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Climate change represents one of the most significant challenges facing humanity. The scientific consensus indicates that human activities are the primary driver of global warming, with greenhouse gas emissions from fossil fuel combustion being the main contributor.",
  "context": {
    "domain": "environmental science",
    "contentType": "research article"
  }
}

### 6. Individual Metric Scoring - Usefulness
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/usefulness
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "To improve your productivity, start by identifying your most important tasks using the Eisenhower Matrix. Categorize activities into four quadrants: urgent and important, important but not urgent, urgent but not important, and neither urgent nor important. Focus on the first two quadrants for maximum effectiveness.",
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "professionals",
    "purpose": "provide productivity tips",
    "tone": "instructional"
  }
}

### 7. Batch Quality Evaluation
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/batch
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "requests": [
    {
      "content": "Machine learning models require large datasets for training. The quality and quantity of data directly impact model performance. Data preprocessing is a critical step that involves cleaning, normalization, and feature engineering.",
      "criteria": {
        "targetAudience": "data scientists",
        "purpose": "explain ML data requirements"
      }
    },
    {
      "content": "Customer relationship management (CRM) systems help businesses manage interactions with current and potential customers. These tools streamline processes and improve customer satisfaction through better communication and service delivery.",
      "criteria": {
        "targetAudience": "business managers",
        "purpose": "explain CRM benefits"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### 8. Regenerate Low-Quality Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/regenerate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "AI is good. It helps people. Companies use AI. It makes things better. AI will be more important later.",
  "feedback": {
    "overall": 4.2,
    "clarity": 5.0,
    "relevance": 4.0,
    "depth": 3.0,
    "usefulness": 4.8,
    "breakdown": {
      "clarity": {
        "score": 5.0,
        "suggestions": ["Use more varied sentence structures", "Add transitional phrases"]
      },
      "depth": {
        "score": 3.0,
        "suggestions": ["Add more detailed explanations", "Include specific examples"]
      }
    }
  },
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "business professionals",
    "purpose": "explain AI business value",
    "tone": "professional"
  },
  "maxAttempts": 3
}

### 9. Improve Clarity
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/improve/clarity
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "The system processes data. It uses algorithms. The results are displayed. Users can interact with the interface. The system updates automatically.",
  "feedback": {
    "overall": 5.5,
    "clarity": 4.2,
    "breakdown": {
      "clarity": {
        "score": 4.2,
        "suggestions": ["Combine related ideas", "Use better transitions", "Vary sentence structure"]
      }
    }
  }
}

### 10. Improve Relevance
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/improve/relevance
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Technology has changed many industries. Companies adopt new solutions. This creates opportunities for growth. Innovation drives progress.",
  "feedback": {
    "overall": 5.8,
    "relevance": 4.5,
    "breakdown": {
      "relevance": {
        "score": 4.5,
        "suggestions": ["Include industry-specific examples", "Address target audience pain points", "Add relevant keywords"]
      }
    }
  },
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "healthcare executives",
    "purpose": "explain healthcare technology trends",
    "keywords": ["healthcare", "technology", "digital transformation", "patient care"]
  }
}

### 11. Improve Depth
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/improve/depth
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Social media marketing is important. Businesses use platforms like Facebook and Twitter. They post content to engage users. This helps with brand awareness.",
  "feedback": {
    "overall": 5.2,
    "depth": 3.8,
    "breakdown": {
      "depth": {
        "score": 3.8,
        "suggestions": ["Add statistical evidence", "Include case studies", "Explain underlying mechanisms"]
      }
    }
  }
}

### 12. Improve Usefulness
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/improve/usefulness
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Time management is a skill. People should learn to manage their time better. This helps them be more productive. Many struggle with this.",
  "feedback": {
    "overall": 5.9,
    "usefulness": 4.2,
    "breakdown": {
      "usefulness": {
        "score": 4.2,
        "suggestions": ["Provide specific action steps", "Include practical examples", "Add measurable outcomes"]
      }
    }
  },
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "students",
    "purpose": "teach time management techniques"
  }
}

### 13. Get Improvement Suggestions
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/suggestions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "score": {
    "overall": 6.2,
    "clarity": 7.5,
    "relevance": 5.8,
    "depth": 4.9,
    "usefulness": 6.6,
    "breakdown": {
      "relevance": {
        "score": 5.8,
        "suggestions": ["Better target audience alignment", "Include more relevant examples"]
      },
      "depth": {
        "score": 4.9,
        "suggestions": ["Add more detailed analysis", "Include supporting evidence"]
      }
    }
  }
}

### 14. Check if Regeneration is Needed
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/check-threshold
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "score": {
    "overall": 6.5,
    "clarity": 7.2,
    "relevance": 6.8,
    "depth": 5.9,
    "usefulness": 6.1
  },
  "thresholds": {
    "minimum": 7.0
  }
}

### 15. Quick Evaluation - Blog Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/blog-post
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
