}

### 20. Quick Generic Evaluation
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/quick
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Sustainable business practices are no longer optional in today's economy. Companies that prioritize environmental responsibility and social impact are seeing increased customer loyalty and employee satisfaction. This shift toward conscious capitalism is reshaping corporate strategies worldwide.",
  "contentType": "article",
  "targetAudience": "business leaders"
}

### 21. High-Quality Content Example (Should Pass)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/evaluate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "The integration of artificial intelligence in healthcare delivery systems represents a paradigm shift in medical practice. Machine learning algorithms now assist physicians in diagnosing diseases with unprecedented accuracy, analyzing complex medical images and identifying patterns that might escape human observation. For instance, AI systems can detect early-stage cancers from mammograms with accuracy rates exceeding 95%, potentially saving countless lives through early intervention. Furthermore, natural language processing applications enable healthcare providers to extract meaningful insights from unstructured clinical notes, facilitating better patient care coordination and personalized treatment strategies. The convergence of these technologies not only improves diagnostic precision but also optimizes resource allocation, reduces healthcare costs, and enhances patient outcomes across diverse medical specialties.",
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "healthcare professionals",
    "purpose": "inform about AI in healthcare",
    "keywords": ["AI", "healthcare", "diagnostics", "machine learning", "patient care"],
    "tone": "professional"
  },
  "thresholds": {
    "minimum": 7,
    "excellent": 8.5
  }
}

### 22. Low-Quality Content Example (Should Trigger Regeneration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/evaluate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "AI is new tech. It helps doctors. Computers can see sick people. This is good. AI will get better. More hospitals will use it. Patients will like it. It costs money but helps people.",
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "healthcare professionals",
    "purpose": "inform about AI in healthcare",
    "keywords": ["AI", "healthcare", "diagnostics", "patient care"],
    "tone": "professional"
  },
  "thresholds": {
    "minimum": 7,
    "excellent": 8.5
  }
}

### 23. Test with Different Content Types
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/quick
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "To maximize your LinkedIn engagement, post consistently during peak hours (Tuesday-Thursday, 9-11 AM), use relevant hashtags, and encourage comments by asking questions. Include multimedia content and respond to comments within 2 hours to boost visibility.",
  "contentType": "social_media",
  "targetAudience": "marketing professionals"
}

