POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/evaluate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "test audience"
  }
}

### 26. Get System Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/info

### 27. Performance Test - Longer Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "The digital transformation of modern enterprises represents one of the most significant business phenomena of the 21st century. Organizations across all sectors are rapidly adopting cloud computing, artificial intelligence, and Internet of Things (IoT) technologies to remain competitive in an increasingly digital marketplace. This transformation extends beyond mere technological adoption; it fundamentally reshapes business models, organizational structures, and customer relationships. Companies that successfully navigate this digital shift often experience improved operational efficiency, enhanced customer experiences, and new revenue streams. However, the journey requires careful planning, substantial investment, and a cultural shift toward digital-first thinking. Leaders must balance innovation with stability, ensuring that digital initiatives align with core business objectives while maintaining regulatory compliance and cybersecurity standards. The rewards are substantial for those who persevere: increased market share, improved agility, and sustainable growth in an era where digital competence determines market leadership.",
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "business executives",
    "purpose": "explain digital transformation",
    "keywords": ["digital transformation", "cloud computing", "AI", "IoT", "business strategy"],
    "tone": "professional"
  }
}

### 28. Test with Custom Thresholds
POST {{baseUrl}}/quality-scoring/evaluate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Machine learning algorithms are becoming increasingly sophisticated, enabling computers to perform complex tasks that previously required human intelligence. These systems learn from data patterns and improve over time without explicit programming.",
  "criteria": {
    "targetAudience": "technical audience",
    "purpose": "explain ML basics"
  },
  "thresholds": {
    "minimum": 8.0,
    "excellent": 9.0
  }
}
